naughty list because of what happened?

777
00:53:00,310 --> 00:53:03,279
We'll just see how you
guys do this coming year.

778
00:53:03,480 --> 00:53:07,211
- And you, Veronica Jean Campbell.
- Yes, sir?

779
00:53:07,417 --> 00:53:10,352
Science has its place,
but so does magic.

780
00:53:10,554 --> 00:53:11,612
It's just the way it is.

781
00:53:11,821 --> 00:53:14,483
- Thank you, Santa.
- So you don't need me to stick around...

782
00:53:14,691 --> 00:53:18,491
...for a press conference, right?
- I think we're satisfied that you're real.

783
00:53:19,563 --> 00:53:22,225
We're all set over here.
Ready when you are, sir.

784
00:53:22,432 --> 00:53:25,060
- But how about that picture?
- Okay, just one.

785
00:53:26,236 --> 00:53:28,864
- Say chess.
- Chess!

786
00:53:29,072 --> 00:53:31,438
And now, we'd best be on our way.

787
00:53:31,641 --> 00:53:35,008
We'll have to hurry if we're gonna
get everything delivered in time.

788
00:53:36,379 --> 00:53:39,109
Oh, Santa, is there
anything we can do to help?

789
00:53:39,316 --> 00:53:41,978
Well, actually, there is.
May I borrow your wand?

790
00:53:42,185 --> 00:53:45,586
- Of course.
- This thing just might save me tonight.

791
00:53:45,789 --> 00:53:46,813
Go, Santa, go.

792
00:53:47,023 --> 00:53:50,550
Oh, by the way, I think Trevor likes you,
but what do I know?

793
00:53:50,760 --> 00:53:51,886
I'm just Santa Claus.

794
00:53:52,095 --> 00:53:54,029
This ought to speed things up.

795
00:53:54,898 --> 00:53:56,798
Wow, that wand really
turns up the speed.

796
00:53:57,000 --> 00:53:59,798
All right, gang, let's shake a hoof.

797
00:54:00,003 --> 00:54:02,301
Thanks for everything, Santa.

798
00:54:02,505 --> 00:54:07,772
Happy Christmas to all,
and to all a good night!

799
