We had better return
that laser tout de suite.

800
00:55:46,509 --> 00:55:47,567
What's the rush?

801
00:55:47,777 --> 00:55:49,210
We're already grounded for life.

802
00:55:49,412 --> 00:55:51,573
I thought you really wanted that wand.

803
00:55:51,781 --> 00:55:54,944
Yeah, I did,
but Christmas is about giving.

804
00:55:55,151 --> 00:55:56,846
Yeah.

805
00:55:57,053 --> 00:55:59,715
- Sorry I locked you up.
- It's okay.

806
00:55:59,923 --> 00:56:01,220
It all worked out in the end.

807
00:56:01,424 --> 00:56:05,588
So, Miss Logical Science Brain, are you
ready to admit that I was right all along?

808
00:56:05,795 --> 00:56:07,592
I thought I did.

809
00:56:07,797 --> 00:56:09,355
Let me hear it just one more time.

810
00:56:09,566 --> 00:56:12,057
You still have to prove to me
this all really happened.

811
00:56:12,268 --> 00:56:16,034
This could all be a dream,
in which case, it's been a good one.

812
00:56:17,841 --> 00:56:20,207
- Hey, you can't do that.
- Just did.

813
00:56:20,410 --> 00:56:21,638
Wait up!

814
00:56:25,949 --> 00:56:27,507
Trevor.

815
00:56:27,717 --> 00:56:30,777
Wake up, Mr. Sleepyhead.
It's Christmas morning.

816
00:56:30,987 --> 00:56:33,751
We were expecting to see you
at Grandma's last night.

817
00:56:33,957 --> 00:56:36,892
- What happened?
- Mom, Dad, you'll never believe it.

818
00:56:37,093 --> 00:56:38,856
That comet you spotted, Lefreeze...

819
00:56:39,062 --> 00:56:42,498
