836
00:57:51,301 --> 00:57:54,293
How was work, big boy?

837
00:57:55,605 --> 00:57:58,597
- Oh, boy.
- So did you run into Lefreeze?

838
00:57:58,808 --> 00:58:00,002
More like he ran into me.

839
00:58:00,210 --> 00:58:02,542
Oh, you just need a good night's sleep,
