840
00:58:02,745 --> 00:58:04,042
I think I need x-rays.

841
00:58:04,247 --> 00:58:05,475
It went that well, huh?

842
00:58:05,682 --> 00:58:10,517
Let's just say last night gets an
entire chapter in my autobiography.

843
00:58:10,720 --> 00:58:14,178
So where can a guy find
a sandwich around here?

844
00:58:23,099 --> 00:58:24,760
No, thanks.

845
00:58:24,968 --> 00:58:26,401
You're a good Santa.

846
00:58:37,647 --> 00:58:39,672
So there you have it. Crazy, huh?

847
00:58:39,883 --> 00:58:42,613
Told you this holiday special
would be a little different.

848
00:58:42,819 --> 00:58:46,550
Sure, me and my friends
sang a couple songs...

849
00:58:47,323 --> 00:58:49,382
...hung out with Santa Claus...

850
00:58:49,592 --> 00:58:53,221
...saved Christmas
from a crazy giant ice monster.

851
00:58:54,464 --> 00:58:55,931
That's all part of the genre.

852
00:58:56,132 --> 00:58:58,362
No, the thing you've got
to give us credit for...

853
00:58:58,568 --> 00:59:02,902
