done that in a holiday special before.

856
00:59:09,212 --> 00:59:10,474
Ask me why I did it.

857
00:59:10,680 --> 00:59:12,375
Go on, ask.

858
00:59:12,582 --> 00:59:15,915
No, it wasn't to make Veronica kiss me.

859
00:59:16,119 --> 00:59:17,143
<i>Hey.</i>

860
00:59:17,353 --> 00:59:19,981
Although that wasn't so bad.

861
00:59:20,189 --> 00:59:22,680
