864
00:59:29,098 --> 00:59:30,793
<i>Visual reference.</i>

865
00:59:31,000 --> 00:59:36,336
I'm sure there are skeptics out there
who will say it was all just a dream.

866
00:59:36,539 --> 00:59:39,702
